    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content </head>
      <p>Leaves his wife, Lucy, his land and other estate during her lifetime. At her death,
                lea ves eldest son, Benjamin, house and land, other estate and slaves to be divided
                among remaining children, John, Edward and William. Ap points Robert Armistead, John
                Patrick and Lucy Wright executors. Witnessed by Robert and Susan Stacy; probated in
                York County. Robert Armistead and John Patrick refusing to serve as executors, Lucy
                Wright will serve, with Edward Patrick and Robert Manson as sureties. Witnessed by
                R{obert} H{all} Waller. Copy m ade by Samuel Sheild. </p>
    </scopecontent>
